osvSchema.details: Transient DOS in WLAN Host while doing channel switch announcement (CSA), when a mobile station receives invalid channel in CSA IE.

description_data.value: Transient DOS in WLAN Host while doing channel switch announcement (CSA), when a mobile station receives invalid channel in CSA IE.

descriptions.value: Transient DOS in WLAN Host while doing channel switch announcement (CSA), when a mobile station receives invalid channel in CSA IE.
Un ataque de denegación de servicios (DOS) transitorio en el componente WLAN Host mientras realiza el anuncio de cambio de canal (CSA), cuando una estación móvil recibe un canal no válido en CSA IE.
